      "Text": "Security update for haproxy",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for haproxy fixes the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2026-33555: improper validation when matching a received body length to a previously announced `Content-Length`\n  can lead to request smuggling due to HTTP/3 parser desynchronization (bsc#1262103).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
